Lot more kids.
You're gonna love it.

45
00:01:42,269 --> 00:01:43,369
- An apartment.

46
00:01:43,370 --> 00:01:44,770
- That's right.

47
00:01:44,772 --> 00:01:48,708
It's gonna be so much better
than this big, creaky...

48
