- Good.

137
00:06:04,898 --> 00:06:06,198
- Why good?

138
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,800
- Because you told me
that you would stay with me

139
00:06:07,801 --> 00:06:12,801
no matter what, and when you
keep things like that from me,

140
00:06:12,806 --> 00:06:15,666
it makes me wonder.

